FakeProfilePicture.en: Attention! You did not use a picture that clearly shows your face for your main profile image. You have been temporarily blocked by the system and cannot get matched[失望]. Please update your picture to get more likes!
FakeProfilePicture.zh: 注意！由于没有使用可看清脸的真实照片作为头像，你被系统暂时屏蔽了，无法得到配对[失望]。请尽快更新照片，得到更多人的喜欢吧！

PokeReply.en: This is Tantan team account. We greatly value and would love to hear your feedback. We will try our best to solve any problems asap and get back to you!
PokeReply.zh: 遇到什么不爽的事么，快跟探探说说，探探一定为你解决！

ReportedUserBanned.en: The user {{name}} that you reported has been banned from Tantan and has been removed from your match list. Thanks a lot for helping us improving the atmosphere of Tantan!
ReportedUserBanned.zh: 亲，你举报的用户{{name}}已经被探探封号，且从你的聊天列表永远消失啦，握爪感谢！

Welcome.en: Hello {{name}}, welcome to Tantan! Swipe right to like and left to dislike. If someone you liked also likes you back you will be matched! Only matched users can chat with each other. This is our team account. Ask us any questions and we will try our best to get back to you asap!
Welcome.zh: {{name}}，你好，我是探探小助手，探探特别开心又多了一个小伙伴。看照片点赞，互赞就可以聊天。祝愿大家能找到聊得来的朋友，开启心动的约会。遇到的不爽也可以跟我吐槽～也欢迎你对探探的建议哦！

WrongGender.en: We have noticed that the gender you selected does not match your profile pictures. You have therefore been hidden from other users. Please adjust to your correct gender in settings and you will become visible again.
WrongGender.zh: 注意！你的性别填写错了，系统已经暂时屏蔽了你[失望]。请尽快更改，不然无法得到配对哦。
